In order to use this brightness control executable, compile it using gcc and move it to your bin folder.

Example:

gcc -o brc brc.c
chmod +x brc
sudo mv brc /usr/bin/
sudo chown root brc
sudo chmod u+s brc

You can run brc --help for more info.

Then you can use that in your wm config for controlling brightness.

Credits to Eric Waller (ewwaller+code@gmail.com)
